# Coordinate & Unit Conventions

- **Units**: Default to **Meters (m)**. Check `UsdGeom.GetStageMetersPerUnit(stage)` if values seem off.
- **Coordinate System**: Isaac Sim uses **Z-up** by default. Ensure all vector operations (Gf.Vec3d) follow this.
- **Orientation**: Use `Quaternions` in `[w, x, y, z]` format (standard for omni.isaac.core), NOT `[x, y, z, w]` (standard for ROS).

### Math Best Practice
- Use `omni.isaac.core.utils.rotations` for Euler-to-Quat conversions to ensure compatibility with the Isaac Sim backend.